Dragonite (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0148: Dragonair
Pokémon
#0150: Mewtwo →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Dragonite (TCG Pocket).

Dragonite has been featured on 34 different cards since it debuted in the Fossil expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Dragonite cards are normally Dragon-type Stage 2 Pokémon. As a Dragon-type, their attacks have costs including and Energy.
